12::[Experience]::
2Experience (xp) is used to measure how long a player has before he/she achieves the next level. 
12::[How do I check my XP?]::
2Syntax: 12!xp
2This command will display how much XP you have in the format of current / amount needed to level
12::[How do I increase my xp?]::
2Xp can be earned by killing monsters and clearing adventures.  